ecific bone-mineral-density gains the lighter loads cannot replicate. Critical past 40.\",\n    citation: \"Watson et al. (2018) J Bone Miner Res 33(2):211\",\n    tag: \"BONE\"\n  }, {\n    title: \"Endocrine Disruptors in Cosmetics\",\n    body: \"Parabens and phthalates absorb transdermally and detectably alter testosterone, estradiol, and thyroid hormone. Audit your bathroom shelf.\",\n    citation: \"Meeker et al. (2011) Environ Health Perspect 119(2):252\",\n    tag: \"TOXINS\"\n  }];\n\n  /* ---------- Workouts (FORGE) ---------- */\n\n  const FOCUS_META = {\n    fatburn: {\n      label: \"FAT BURN\",\n      color: \"#ff6a00\"\n    },\n    performance: {\n      label: \"PERFORMANCE\",\n      color: \"#0ea5e9\"\n    },\n    strength: {\n      label: \"STRENGTH\",\n      color: \"#f5b400\"\n    },\n    metcon: {\n      label: \"METCON\",\n      color: \"#dc2626\"\n    },\n    mobility: {\n      label: \"MOBILITY\",\n      color: \"#22c55e\"\n    },\n    recovery: {\n      label: \"RECOVERY\",\n      color: \"#9a9a9a\"\n    }\n  };\n  const SU = \"squat university\"; // default form-tutorial channel\n\n  const WORKOUTS = [\n  // ===== FAT BURN (6) =====\n  {\n    id: \"tabata-torch\",\n    name: \"TABATA TORCH\",\n    time: 4,\n    focus: \"fatburn\",\n    intensity: \"max\",\n    description: \"Maximal-output 4-minute protocol. 8 rounds of 20s all-out / 10s rest.\",\n    scienceNote: \"The original Tabata study showed VO₂max gains equal to 1hr of moderate cycling, in 4 minutes — provided each 20s round is genuine all-out effort (170%+ VO₂max).\",\n    citation: \"Tabata et al. (1996) Med Sci Sports Exerc 28(10):1327\",\n    exercises: [{\n      name: \"Burpee (8 rounds)\",\n      setsReps: \"20s ON / 10s OFF × 8\",\n      cue: \"Chest to floor every rep. No pacing.\",\n      videoQuery: \"burpee form tutorial \" + SU\n    }]\n  }, {\n    id: \"post-meal-walk\",\n    name: \"POST-PRANDIAL SIPHON\",\n    time: 10,\n    focus: \"fatburn\",\n    intensity: \"low\",